        <title>How to Tell If Your CEO Is Clueless</title>
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://blog.guykawasaki.com/2008/10/our-team-is-tot.html" />
        <link rel="replies" type="text/html" href="http://blog.guykawasaki.com/2008/10/our-team-is-tot.html" thr:count="0" />
